2026-06-23 21:02:26,108 DEBUG msg #26: UserMessage tool_result(toolu_01Nx6PuTeoErF5Dm4mninNuS): 1	"""Bracket builder: generates a World Cup knockout bracket TOML from live standings/teams."""
